title: Faith No More LIVE at Download Festival (AWESOME AUDIO QUALITY!)
description:
Thanks to RevJonn for providing source material (ripped from live stream).

This is the first torrent I have EVER created and shared. I hope it works well for you and PLEASE comment if it's got any errors or problems so I can fix it.

I've cut each track separately and FULLY TAGGED it but (and here's the best part) I've re-worked the EQ's on the entire show and cleaned it up so it sounds INCREDIBLE. Not just a straight-up copy; this baby has been ENHANCED and levels mixed to make it much more listenable, enjoyable, and sound better in your car, home, or wherever you listen to it. I preserved the original bitrates from RevJonn so there is no loss in quality. Had to borrow a little from Chipsteak's torrent as well due to some errors in tracks 5&6 and fill it all in as such, but ultimately it all sounds mixed well together.

On a side note: GODDAMN IT, it's GREAT to hear Faith No More back together after all of these years! Now TOUR THE USA, DUDES!!!
